<component id="slide01">
<text><![CDATA[<font size="14"><b><ul><li>A VPN is a private network that is created via tunneling over a public network, usually the Internet.</li><br/><li>There are site-to-site VPNs and remote access VPNs.</li><br/><li>VPNs require the use of modern encryption techniques to ensure secure transport of information.</li></ul></b></font>]]></text>
</component>




